      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i am planning a trip to a big city soon and i cant decide where to stay. can u compare the vibe of a place like Upper Heights (which is super upscale and mostly white) vs something like the East River district (more diverse and lower income)? like, which one is more \"welcoming\" for a tourist who wants a good experience?",
